## Coordinate System

- NDC (Normalised Device Coordinates): X ∈ [−1, 1], Y ∈ [−1, 1], Z ∈ [0, 1].
- **Y-axis points upward** in NDC — the top of the screen is `y = +1`.
- Vertices outside these ranges are silently clipped.

