## Common Pitfalls

| Pitfall | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Forgetting `COPY_SRC` on output buffers | Add `wgpu.BufferUsage.COPY_SRC` when you need `read_buffer()`. |
| Binding index mismatch | Ensure `@binding(N)` in WGSL matches `"binding": N` in `create_bind_group`. |
| Wrong `bytes_per_row` for textures | Must be a multiple of 256 when copying textures via the queue. |
| Y-axis confusion | Screen top → NDC `y = +1`; screen bottom → NDC `y = -1`. |
| Shared vs per-frame device | Use `get_default_device()` so all modules share the same device. |
| Mutating a `memoryview` return | Call `.copy()` or `np.frombuffer(raw, ...).copy()` before modifying. |

